Ludivine Sagnier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ludivine_Sagnier 0 Ludivine Sagnier (born July 3, 1979) is a French actress and model, who has appeared in films since 1989. She was nominated for two César Awards for Best Supporting Actress in Swimming Pool (2003) and Un secret (2007).
